## 1. Brand Colors

| Name             | HEX       | RGB         | Usage |
|------------------|-----------|-------------|-------|
| **Signal Orange**| `#FF7400` | 255,116,0   | Primary CTAs, key highlights, important badges, active states, critical KPIs. Avoid large background fills. |
| **Deep Navy**    | `#0B1F8B` | 11,31,139   | Brand background, hero sections, headers/footers, nav bars, primary typography on light backgrounds. |
| **Concrete Gray**| `#F2FKF7` | 242,252,247 | Neutral section backgrounds, cards, form fields, subtle separation between UI blocks. |
| **Charcoal**     | `#102830` | 16,40,48    | Primary text color, icons, dark UI elements, dividers, outlines. |
| **Emerald**      | `#1F4F43` | 31,79,67    | Success/positive states, environmental KPIs, secondary chart accents. |

